A humble presentation of an excellent contribution from
[DaffMakes](https://cults3d.com/en/users/DaffMakes/3d-models), reworking excellent original designs by Moonjammy, DangitBobby, and Woddish.

Need some more hatch options to keep your Legions of tanks looking fresh? How's about 45 new options!

Including:
- Tank Commanders in 6 poses
- Pintle Gunners with 3 weapon options
- All options come in 5 Galactic Crusader armour styles
- All options come in Windowed hatches (suitable for most vehicles) or Riveted hatches (suitable for Sig-RN vehicles)

TODO:
- Support Riveted options
- Add Lychee file (_The file I was working on decided to self-destruct

*Like what... DaffMakes is doing!? Check out his [Cults page](https://cults3d.com/en/users/DaffMakes/3d-models), where he's breathing new life into the Galactic Crusaders, or his [Ko-Fi](https://ko-fi.com/daffmakes)*
